<h2 id="quick-reference">Sugar Quantity Quick Reference  <a class="anchor" href="#quick-reference">{% icon "link" %}</a></h2>

<p>It can be shocking to discover just how much sugar, fruit juice concentrate and <abbr title="High Fructose Corn Syrup">HFCS</abbr> is included in drinks, condiments, bread and more. Read the label. Check out the below charts for a quick reference to a very short list of common drinks and foods.</p>

